{{Infobox legislation |short_title = Sindh Local Government Ordinance, 2001 |legislature = [[Sindh Assembly]] |image = |imagesize = 100px |imagealt = |caption = |long_title = An Ordinance to reconstruct and regulate the local governments |citation = [https://web.archive.org/web/20170702144550/http://www.sindh.gov.pk/dpt/services/RULES/SLGO%202001%20_February03_.pdf Ordinance No. XXVI of 2001] |territorial_extent = Whole of [[Sindh]] except [[Cantonment (Pakistan)|cantonments]] |enacted_by = Provincial Assembly of Sindh |date_passed = August 14th, 2001 |date_enacted = |enacted_by2 = |date_enacted2 = |date_passed2 = |date_assented = |royal_assent = |date_commenced = |bill = |bill_citation = |bill_date = |introduced_by = |1st_reading = |2nd_reading = |3rd_reading = |committee_report = |bill2 = |bill_citation2 = |bill_date2 = |introduced_by2 = |1st_reading2 = |2nd_reading2 = |3rd_reading2 = |committee_report2 = |white_paper = |amendments = |repeals = |date_repealed = July 14th, 2011 ([[Sindh (Repeal of the Sindh Local Government Ordinance, 2001 and Revival of the Sindh Local Government Ordinance, 1979) Act, 2011]], Act No. XXIV of 2011, [http://www.pas.gov.pk/index.php/acts/details/en/19/153 No. PAS/Legis-B-25/2011]) |related_legislation = |summary = |keywords = |status = repealed }}
The '''Sindh Local Government Ordinance, 2001''' was an [[Local ordinance|ordinance]] passed by the [[Provincial Assembly of Sindh]] on August 14th, 2001, as part of a series of local government ordinances prepared by the [[National Reconstruction Bureau]] passed together by each of the four provinces at the time.
The ordinance was repealed with an [[Sindh (Repeal of the Sindh Local Government Ordinance, 2001 and Revival of the Sindh Local Government Ordinance, 1979) Act, 2011|act restoring the local government ordinance of 1979]] by acting Governor [[Nisar Ahmed Khuhro]] following a political row between the [[Pakistan Peoples Party|PPP]] and [[MQM]] over statements made by Dr. [[Zulfiqar Mirza]].<ref name="tribune">{{cite news|title=Government repeals Sindh local government act, MQM protests|url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/510520/government-repeals-sindh-local-government-act-mqm-protests/|date=2013-02-21|place=Karachi, Pakistan|access-date=2018-05-23|newspaper=[[The Express Tribune]]}}</ref>
